Uses of Package
org.jsonurl

  • Packages that use org.jsonurl 
    Package Description
    org.jsonurl
    Provides the base interfaces, classes, and exceptions needed to parse the JSON→URL grammar.
    org.jsonurl.factory
    Defines generic value factory and parser interfaces, and provides a parser implementation built on the JsonUrlIterator interface.
    org.jsonurl.j2se
    A JSON→URL parser and text generator based J2SE datatypes.
    org.jsonurl.jsonorg
    A JSON→URL parser and text generator based on Douglas Crockford's original Java implementation of JSON.
    org.jsonurl.jsonp
    A JSON→URL parser and text generator based on the JSON-P interface defined by JSR-374.
    org.jsonurl.stream
    Provides a streaming interface for parsing JSON→URL text.
    org.jsonurl.text
    Provides interfaces and base support for generating JSON→URL text.

    BigMathProvider

    Enumeration of BigInteger overflow operations.
    CompositeType
    An enumeration of JSON→URL composite types.
    JsonUrlLimits
    JSON→URL text parse limits.
    JsonUrlLimits.Builder
    JSON→URL text limit builder.
    JsonUrlOption
    An enumeration of JSON→URL options available to both parsing and serialization.
    LimitException
    A exception that occurs when a limit is exceeded.
    LimitException.Message
    Enumeration of messages.
    ParseException
    An exception that occurs while parsing JSON→URL text.
    SyntaxException
    A syntax error in JSON→URL text.
    SyntaxException.Message
    Enumeration of messages.
    ValueType
    An enumeration of JSON→URL value types.
